Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:06.66,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}Right in front of me, all the stars that take the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:12.50,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}a million lights surround me with their soft embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:18.34,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}あの頃　信じてた世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:24.68,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}今もまだ正しいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:30.98,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}I know for certain now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:37.73,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}彷徨う僕たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:41.36,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}手探りでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:46.99,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}愛を感じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:52.67,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}Oh all the visions living in your memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:58.59,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}Will you remember me as you loved me？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:05.14,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}どんな形でも　代わりはないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:09.89,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}キミとなら紡げる Love Story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:18.90,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}微笑み合う日を重ねたい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.45,0:22:06.66,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}繁星就在眼前  铺满整片夜空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.66,0:22:12.50,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}无数光芒将我拥入怀中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.50,0:22:18.34,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}曾经笃信的理想世界
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.34,0:22:24.68,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}如今是否还处于正轨
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.30,0:22:30.98,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}此刻我已经确信
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.98,0:22:37.73,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}彷徨无助的我们
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.73,0:22:41.36,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}哪怕不断摸索
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.74,0:22:46.99,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}也要触碰爱的温度
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.99,0:22:52.67,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}记忆深处  景象万千
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.67,0:22:58.59,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}可还记得  你曾深爱的我
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.59,0:23:05.14,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}无论何种形态  终是无可替代
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.14,0:23:09.89,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}与你携手  才能织成爱的诗篇
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.22,0:23:18.90,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}愿欢笑与我们久久为伴
